message.body: Hey FYI I'm not dead. And I miss you
I was getting ready to finally email you last week and then my asshole laptop died
So now I'm limbo for a few more days until the new one arrives
Things have been obscenely busy lately
Haha! I figured you are having a wild busy summer! Boo to laptop death but hurray for a new one. I bought one this month
I'm forcing myself to decide which one to get tonight
I hate spending money
Me too. Ugh
Are all yr friends getting married this summer?
It's so hard to justify spending $2k for a 15 inch when I just use it as a tv
We got a TV finally so my new laptop just sits there cause I'm too cheap to get adobe cloud
The duffy sisters are a whirlwind of drama and anxiety for me
I know I'm too cheap for that too!!
I've only had one this summer thank god. It was pretty fun. Brandon and I are about to see NIN and sound garden tonight
OMG that is so awesome!
Lol. It's at a huge stadium. I asked if we could leave at 11 no matter what.
That was my condition for going
Hahaha whatever you'll be there for all the encores
Hahahahahaha
Let me know if you have any free time for hanging/visits between now and early October
Funny you should say that, VCU is flying me down for a lecture. Date still pending but will be late December or early October
Oh sweet
I'll let you know for sure. Wanna make a weekend of it
I have family vacation Labor Day week and I think Annie's bridal shower is sept 20 I think
Then her bachelorette weekend will be some time in sept/oct
cool! Ill let you know the form date ASAP. If it doesn't work out you come up here!!!
Are you planning the whole wedding?!
Ugh I think so
Lol so much work
Yeah I'd totally be up for a visit to Philly soon
We've been working 4 day work weeks this summer which has ruled
Aside from me making less $
That is awesome. My summer class ends Saturday then I'm doing a quick DC trip and a Vermont trip before class starts back up the 25th
But I'm assuming my life will be shit town after October since work will be nuts and Annie's wedding is the first week of nov
Yeah. You know it will be.
I'm heading out but let's KIT about a visit!
Yeah we'll figure something out! Have fun tonight!!
Thanks! Talk soon!
